    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/209aa09b0732f4bfd3aa41d7ab27aa01.avif?t=1769654309\" width=750 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/1a885c120e0331287770b7635a55aab6.poster.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/1a885c120e0331287770b7635a55aab6.webm?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/1a885c120e0331287770b7635a55aab6.mp4?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地狱真菌蔓延，污染大地。</strong>卵石之王率领一支勇敢的骑士部族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五颗卵石在混乱逼近时觉醒。黑夜迅速降临，忘却恐惧吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗来袭，战斗开始。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/de393111a5590b1645eaae82b92802e1.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/69c92fadc908c16f5788ea0e43e71327.poster.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/69c92fadc908c16f5788ea0e43e71327.webm?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/69c92fadc908c16f5788ea0e43e71327.mp4?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造更强的装备，掌握狂野的技能。挖掘矿石，升级你的王国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >携手作战，扭转命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快点行动，黑夜比你想象的更快降临！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/46e405f91ab3be402d6b457eccbff119.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/177d303e65bad96228baf2c649399297.poster.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/177d303e65bad96228baf2c649399297.webm?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/177d303e65bad96228baf2c649399297.mp4?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>霉怪肮脏又强大。霉怪首领？恶心至极，残暴无比。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团结一致，否则就会被碾成卵石尘！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国的命运掌握在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/d1595ff67e440d9796a1ea27600ee180.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/ec320da1468606f29c02d42489954b8a.poster.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/ec320da1468606f29c02d42489954b8a.webm?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/ec320da1468606f29c02d42489954b8a.mp4?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>看到发光的东西了吗？捡起来。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能举得动？那它就是武器。扔出去、挥一挥，或者直接吃了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用任何方式摧毁末日之霉！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/0db0ba46a2d65192fa383d3b5b48752b.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/6bbadb59b6f58b18e013e86e1b2cea29.poster.avif?t=1769654309\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/6bbadb59b6f58b18e013e86e1b2cea29.webm?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087930/extras/6bbadb59b6f58b18e013e86e1b2cea29.mp4?t=1769654309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一刻宁静，转瞬混乱。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奋战漫漫长夜吧，卵石骑士！</strong></p>",
